OL,3,CFurther arrest made after death of
OL,4,Cteenager in Coventry
OL,6,FPolice officers investigating the
OL,7,Fdeath of a teenager in Coventry
OL,8,Fearlier this year have made another
OL,9,Farrest.
OL,11,FMichael Ababio, 18, died after he was
OL,12,Fstabbed near Foleshill Library, on 22
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,FA 24-year-old man was arrested from an
OL,16,Faddress in Hillfields on Monday, June
OL,17,F1, on suspicion of conspiracy to
OL,18,Fmurder. He remains in custody while
OL,19,Fthe investigation continues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
