OL,3,CFurther arrest made after death of
OL,4,Cteenager in Coventry
OL,6,FFour people have so far been charged
OL,7,Fin connection with Mr Ababio's death.
OL,9,FSince then, detectives have worked to
OL,10,Fgather evidence and speak to witnesses
OL,11,Fas part of their investigation.
OL,13,FAnyone who saw what happened and
OL,14,Fhasn't yet come forward to speak can
OL,15,Fdo so by calling 101 quoting log 4185
OL,16,Fof 22 February.
